com.viaoa.web

Class OABackgroundImage

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.viaoa.web.OAHtmlElement
      • com.viaoa.web.OAImage
        • com.viaoa.web.OABackgroundImage
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OAJspComponent, OAJspRequirementsInterface, Serializable

    public class OABackgroundImage
extends OAImage
    Controls an html elements style background-image. Note: This will use css background image styling, and the image will be sized to match the sizing of the element. The size of the image will not affect the size of the html element.
    Author:
    vvia
    See Also:
    Serialized Form
